ACRONYMS:
---------

uTTCOS - Micro Time Triggered Cooperative Operating System

EVR - Event Vector Register

TDD - Test Driven Development

FIO_FLAG_D - Flag Data Register

FIO_POLAR - Flag Polar Register

FIO_INEN - Flag Input Enable Register

FIO_DIR	- Flag Direction Register

EBIU - External Bus Interface Unit

GPIO - General Purpose Input/Output

CPU - Central Processing Unit

CCU - Central Communication Unit

DAB - DMA Access Bus

EAB - External Access Bus

MMR - Memory Mapped Register

DMA - Direct Memory Access

P0 - Pointer Register 0

p0 - Processor 0

